i want to try guiness what does it taste like my friend tried it and hated it so that is why i am asking thanks it just seems so hyped up that you go to a pub you atleast try a pint of guniess coffee and chocolate sounds good i will have to try it sometime it is a very nice beer the beer style is called stout guinness extra stout opaque red brown color with a creamy tawny head very full bodied dense and thick a complex spicy worcestershire sauce aroma dry coffee toffee flavor with a chocolate finish but still dry guinness extra stout draught almost black certainly opaque unless you have a very powerful light source creamy head heavy bodied complex spicy aroma less carbonated than the bottled version smooth mellow extremely well balanced head lasts to the bottom of the glass guinness cream stout extremely deep brown very little co strong burnt malt flavor bitter and flat very harsh it is a unique beer no doubt but if you like coffee or especially cold coffee then you will like guinness stout at least a little but you will be better for the experience enjoy Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Saint Nicholas Monster (manga) James Hanratty Investigation into the bombing of Pan Am Flight 103 Sin City 21 July 2005 London bombings Grumpy's Three Wishes Columbine High School massacre Hundred Years' War Singlish Mothers Against Drunk Driving The Catcher in the Rye The Contender (television series) Ron Weasley Edward VIII of the United Kingdom Age of consent Yu-Gi-Oh! anime and manga characters EastEnders Alternative theories into the bombing of Pan Am Flight 103 AFI 100 Years series Virginia Lewis (The 10th Kingdom) Air India Flight 182 Big Brother UK series 6 Pan Am Flight 103 bombing trial Futurama (TV series - season 3) The Inside The Invisibles Henry IV of France R. Kelly Captain Thunderbolt Silent Night, Deadly Night The Life and Times of Juniper Lee Haven (TNG episode) The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Tertiary to Quintessential Phases Fancy Crane Eddie Guerrero John Sherid